<h3 id="decent-parallax-scrolling">Decent Parallax Scrolling</h3>

<p>Almost invisible at first sight, parallax scrolling applied to big image headers makes them move at a different speed and thus creates an <strong>impression of depth</strong> â€” tiny details essential for a truly polished look and feel.</p>

<h3 id="estimated-reading-duration">Estimated Reading Duration</h3>

<p>Itâ€™s nice to know how long it will take to read a post upfront. Because of that, thereâ€™s an indicator on top of every post which provides an estimate.</p>

