<h3 id="clean-valid-html5--css3">Clean, Valid HTML5 &amp; CSS3</h3>

<p>Clean, optimized, validated &amp; handwritten source code can be taken for granted. <strong>Quality code is just as important as good design</strong> and thereâ€™s no room for compromises.</p>

<p>In addition to that, the entire theme has been carefully tested to achieve best possible <strong>crossbrowser compatibility</strong> and meet highest requirements and so it works just fine in Internet Explorer 9+, Firefox 4+, Safari 5+, Chrome 14+, Opera 10.6+ as well as on iOS 4+ and Android devices.</p>

